Invocation Name: three steps curried eggs
des: Three Steps Curried Eggs.Three steps to make delicious curried eggs using three ingredients. You will need eggs, butter or margarine or sour cream and curry powder. They are very easy to make and can be used as finger food for parties, barbeques, or snacks.
